The speed of processing offline messages has been significantly improved Sending photos and videos in a media message has been made possible Extensive improvement of the reply system to messages: Correct display of replies to messages with attachments. Possibility to add any attachments to the reply as well as to reply with a voice message Jumping to the original message by tapping on the reply if still available in the dialogue Reconnection of calls in case of short network interruptions e.g. change from WLAN to mobile internet Lots of minor improvements

Redesigned personal profile screen Redesigned PIN code entry screen Added the ability to view the profile of the contact who sent the invitation Added channel search by id Added the ability to share a link to a web view channel Fixed incorrect display of the date of the message in some cases Lots of minor improvements

Improved the app protection function with a pin code: now you can set the idle time after which the app will be locked also added an instant lock button Redesigned the application start screen before registering or restoring from a backup Removed dislikes in channels Lots of minor improvements

Added the ability to hide author and content in push notifications settings privacy Fixed bugs when some links or GIFs broke the display of messages grey screen Added donation ability Updated terms of use for clubs

Added the ability to block a contact he will not be able to send you an invitation call or send a message until he is unblocked . To block contact just delete him or use new button in the invite dialogue. Minor improvements

Fixed launch problem on iOS 12 Added group calls up to 4 members Unsuccessfully sent messages now will be re sent Added an ability to go to message from media tabs in profiles Minor bug fixes and interface improvements
